Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph search

search

Purpose:
  Search a Wiki Graph archive for URI-addressable objects.

Usage:
  wikigraph search <archive.sdpub> <query> [--type <entity|triple|source|summary|chunk[,kind...]>] [--chapter <ids>] [--limit <n>] [--cursor <token>] [--json|--jsonl] [--help|-h]

Notes:
  - Results are returned as a linear list of Wiki Graph URIs.
  - Without `--type`, search first looks for entity objects and falls back to text objects when no entity matches.
  - `--type` filters result objects.

Examples:
  wikigraph search book.sdpub "恩典 婴儿洗礼"
  wikigraph search book.sdpub "infant baptism" --type entity --json
